    "description": "浮岛风云（Isles of Etherion） 是一款有着类似暗黑破坏神的战斗系统、类似最终幻想的奇幻世界和100%可破坏体素环境的动作冒险RPG。自由探索一个由诸多浮岛构成，表面色彩缤纷而地下却危机四伏的开放世界。借助基本的飞行能力和滑翔系统，享受独特的垂直探险，游历通常难以到达的角落。使用在冒险过程中获得的不同武器和法术来面对各种类型的敌人。施展强大的有着物理效应的魔法，还能将不同元素属性的法术组合起来实现多种组合效果。任意挖掘隧道寻找隐藏的宝藏与地城，掠夺海盗飞艇将其占为己有，收集散落在各地的圣石碎片以挑战元素半神，结束元素之战让以太世界重新恢复平静。IoE中有7个可选的种族——人类、精灵、矮人、侏儒、仙女、天使和恶魔，每个种族都有自己的优势和劣势。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>100%可动态破坏的体素环境</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/c9f94c1dd43f395aef6792328fcda464.poster.avif?t=1688606719\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/c9f94c1dd43f395aef6792328fcda464.webm?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/c9f94c1dd43f395aef6792328fcda464.mp4?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索一个包括地貌在内所有的东西都可以动态破坏的环境，不光是玩家的行为，怪物行为和自然灾害也能够改变环境。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>飞艇</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/cf4ee2d96ff5372f92c83ad271a3419b.poster.avif?t=1688606719\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/cf4ee2d96ff5372f92c83ad271a3419b.webm?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/cf4ee2d96ff5372f92c83ad271a3419b.mp4?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>驾驶属于你自己的飞艇穿梭于以太群岛之间，而飞艇可以通过买卖或者抢夺来获得。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态季节更换</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/dd66c0a5f18ef3a519627f0de43ca1b4.poster.avif?t=1688606719\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/dd66c0a5f18ef3a519627f0de43ca1b4.webm?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/dd66c0a5f18ef3a519627f0de43ca1b4.mp4?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在以太群岛，随着时间的推移四季动态更迭。白天与黑夜之间，不同的季节之间，同一个地方的怪物类型不尽相同。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自然灾害</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/72dcd9fe7f2a097e0d2ec0730e423085.poster.avif?t=1688606719\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/72dcd9fe7f2a097e0d2ec0730e423085.webm?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/72dcd9fe7f2a097e0d2ec0730e423085.mp4?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>像地震、陨石、飓风、火山喷发这样的自然灾害在IoE的各个角落随机发生。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>体素战斗与法术编织</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/4ac7ba73112c19b1c02c4aa3ba84aac9.poster.avif?t=1688606719\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/4ac7ba73112c19b1c02c4aa3ba84aac9.webm?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771770/extras/4ac7ba73112c19b1c02c4aa3ba84aac9.mp4?t=1688606719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>整个世界都由体素构成。在战斗过程中，可以施展法术改变地貌来获得战斗优势，当然有些敌人也具备这样的技能。IoE里不仅可以操控强大的法力，还可以将不同元素的法术编织起来实现各种不一样的效果。例如，在龙卷风里注入火元素便能形成火焰龙卷风！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>基于元素的因与果</strong></h2>以太群岛所有的东西都有元素属性，包括法术、怪物、武器、物品和浮岛本身。元素之间互相斗争争夺霸权。过多的施展某一元素的法术会将该元素注入周围的环境，进而吸引该元素属性的怪物，改变局部的元素平衡。所以，玩家的每一个行为都有可能改变后续的游玩体验！",
